Wikileaks releases Iraq War Logs, secret American military records which reveal new information, including that U.S. commanders allowed torture and execution to occur without investigation and that hundreds of civilians have been killed at U.S. military checkpoints during the War on Iraq. Hillary Clinton and other U.S. officials condemn the disclosures. (BBC), (New York Times)A suicide bomber attacks the United Nations compound in western Afghanistan based in Herat. (Voice of America)